title: Saints sprint to big lead, hold off Colts' comeback 27-21 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,530 Saints sprint to big lead, hold off Colts' comeback 27-21 (Yahoo Sports) Drew Brees kept Indianapolis off balance all day. Eventually, he was able to finally put away the Colts. After building a 27-point lead, then watching Andrew Luck rally his team within one score, New Orleans recovered an onside kick and Brees ran out the clock to preserve a crucial 27-21 victory at Indianapolis.
